fatal error when WooCommerce Subscriptions deactivates itself<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix a potential warning with WooCommerce Bookings<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.4.2 (2020-05-25)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix variable product removed from the cart when a second browser tab displays the backend<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix variable product removed from the cart when a REST request occurs on front<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix shop pages set as child page<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix PHP warning when the option `woocommerce_bacs_accounts` serialization is corrupted<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix PHP notice when a user resetting his password has a user locale which doesn\'t exist in Polylang<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.4.1 (2020-04-21)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix fatal error on order-received page when no order id is provided.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix the translations status report visible when no languages are defined.<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix PHP notice in wizard.<\\/li>\\n<li>Subscriptions: fix translated slugs of endpoints not working.<\\/li>\\n<li>Subscriptions: fix a conflict with WooCommerce Memberships causing a PHP notice.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.4 (2020-04-06 )<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Requires WooCommerce 3.4 or higher, Polylang 2.7 or higher<\\/li>\\n<li>Don\'t allow users without manage_product_terms permissions to create categories using the product importer<\\/li>\\n<li>Add a WooCommerce step to the wizard<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with WooCommerce Free Gift Coupons<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix new account email sent in wrong language when the language is set from the content<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix variation name in \\\"Pay for order\\\" form<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.3.3 (2020-03-05)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix wrong subject &amp; heading language for emails sent in bulk<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix wrong translation url when the shop is not translated<\\/li>\\n<li>WC Subscriptions: Fix translated variations not deleted when deleting a subscription variation.<\\/li>\\n<li>WC Composite Products: Fix fatal error when creating a new translation when the plugin WC Product Search is activated<\\/li>\\n<li>WC Composite Products: Fix PHP warnings<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.3.2 (2020-02-13)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix paged shop pages redirected to main shop page (introduced in 1.3.1)<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.3.1 (2020-02-11)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Fix fatal error when the product_cat taxonomy is unregistered or in case of DB error<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix language switcher not working for order-pay endpoint<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix canonical redirect for the shop page<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix variations copy when several product variation are using the same attribute<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.3 (2020-01-20)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Requires PHP 5.6 or higher, WordPress 4.9 or higher, WooCommerce 3.2 or higher, Polylang 2.6 or higher<\\/li>\\n<li>Change text domain from \'pllwc\' to \'polylang-wc\'<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with WooCommerce 3.9<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with WooCommerce Composite Products<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with Checkout Field Editor for WooCommerce<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with \\\"All Reviews\\\" block introduced in WC 3.8. Requires Polylang Pro 2.6.9+<\\/li>\\n<li>Add compatibility with \\\"All Products\\\" block introduced in WC 3.9<\\/li>\\n<li>Duplicate media if they don\'t exist when translating a product gallery<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix jQuery undefined if a user decides to load jQuery in the footer<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix duplicated sku error when creating a product translation with the REST API<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix \\\"On sale products\\\" block. Requires Polylang Pro 2.6.9+<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.2.5 (2019-12-26)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>WC Bookings: Translate pending confirmation email<\\/li>\\n<li>WC Bookings: Fix notice when adding a bookable product to the cart<\\/li>\\n<li>Fix order emails not sent in the order language when processed from the order preview.<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.2.4 (2019-11-14)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Add compatibility with Polylang 2.6.7<\\/li>\\n<\\/ul>\\n<p>1.2.3 (2019-11-05)<\\/p>\\n<ul>\\n<li>Add compatibility with WC 3.8, with the exceptio